'''Turkey Tailfeather Woman''' was a [[Sioux|Dakota]] woman who is said to have given the '''Drum Dance''' to the [[Anishinaabe]] people. The Drum Dance is a set of spiritual beliefs that center on Turkey Tailfeather Woman and her escape from the American military, after which she built a large drum while in hiding. The religion spread throughout a large swathe of North America after about 1877. The drum used in the Drum Dance is the forerunner of the large drum used in modern [[powwow]]s.

